        <div class="w96">
          <h1>北京市门头沟区景观大道（滨河路至阜石路辅线段）交通疏堵工程监理项目招标公告</h1>
          <div class="msgbar">发布时间： 2017-11-17 16:25:25 &nbsp; 作者：本站编辑 &nbsp; 浏览次数：<span id="views"></span> &nbsp;  </div>
		  
          <div class="content" style="font-size: 13px">		 		  
            <div style="text-align: center; text-indent: -60pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 60pt" align="center"><span style="color: red; font-size: 12pt">北京市门头沟区景观大道(滨河路至阜石路辅线段）交通疏堵工程</span></div>
<div align="center"><b><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt">监理项目</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt">招标公告</span></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 22pt"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 14.5pt">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -22.2pt; margin: 13pt 0cm 13pt 22.2pt"><b><font size="5"><a name="_Toc247085672"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt"><span>1.&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">招标条件</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal">本招标项目北京市门头沟区景观大道(滨河路至阜石路辅线段）交通疏堵工程监理项目（项目名称）MC2017-194-2（招标编号）已由北京市门头沟区政府采购办公室以MTGXM-201710208830号采购详细计划批准采购，建设资金来自财政拨款（资金来源），项目出资比例为 100% ，招标人为北京市门头沟区市政市容管理委员会。项目已具备招标条件，现对该项目进行公开招标。</span></font></b></div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><a name="_Toc247085673"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">2. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">项目概况与招标范围</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">项目名称：北京市门头沟区景观大道(滨河路至阜石路辅线段）交通疏堵工程监理项目</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">招标编号：MC2017-194-2</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">招标内容：景观大道(滨河路至阜石路辅线段）交通疏堵工程监理</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">招标项目的建设地点：门头沟区</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">规模：<span style="color: black">小型修缮</span></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">计划工期：2018年3月15日至2018年7月5日<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; 110</span>日历天</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">招标范围：设计图纸显示的全部内容</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">财政批复资金：<span style="color: black">监理费控制价：189869.13元</span></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">工程资金来自财政资金，超过工程预算资金的投标将被拒绝</span></div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><a name="_Toc247085674"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: normal">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">投标人资格要求</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 150%">本次招标要求投标人须<a name="_Toc393440363">有<span style="color: red">市政公用工程监理乙级（含）以上资质，并在人员、质量保证管理体系、资金、设备等方面有圆满完成本工程监理工作的能力的充足有效的证明材料。</span></a></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 150%">总监理工程师具有国家注册监理工程师资格（建筑工程专业）及总监任命书<span>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">4. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">招标文件的获取</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 15.75pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><a name="_Toc247085676"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>4.1 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>凡有意参加投标者，请于<b><span>2017年11月17日至2017年11月27日</span></b>9：00----17:00时（北京时间，下同），可在规定的时间内报名参加本项目投标。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 15.75pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>4.2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>、报名地点：北京市门头沟区政府采购中心网站（<span>http：//www.bjmtgcg.cn）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 15.75pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>4.3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>、注意事项本项目采用网上报名，详细报名程序见中心外网资料下载栏目《供应商操作手册》，请按操作手册要求进行投标报名。简要说明如下：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>（<span>1） 参加本项目首先要取得我中心认证，认证事宜请登陆门头沟区政府采购中心网站（http://www.bjmtgcg.cn）。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>（<span>2）确认参加本项目投标，需以用户名和密码登陆《供应商》平台，进行报名。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 31.6pt; margin: 0cm -1.8pt 0pt 0cm; vertical-align: bottom" align="left"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><b><span>报名成功后，请打印《报名成功通知单》并加盖公章，递交投标文件时时出示</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">5. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">投标文件的递交</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt">5.1 投标文件递交的截止时间（投标截止时间，下同）为<u><span> 2017</span></u>年<u>12</u>月<u>8</u>日<u>9</u>时<u>30</u>分，</div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 15.75pt">地点：北京市门头沟区双峪路39-1政府采购中心开标室。</div>
<div style="line-height: 150%"><span style="line-height: 150%">5.2</span><span style="line-height: 150%">投标人法人代表应参加开标会，并携带营业执照副本复印件（加盖公章）及本人身份证，此时拟派项目总监也必须参加开标会。投标人法人代表不能出席开标会，投标人应指定拟派项目总监为委托代理人参加，并须持法人代表授权书及本人身份证原件及复印件（盖公章）、监理工程师注册证书原件及复印件（盖公章）。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt">5.4逾期送达的或者未送达指定地点的投标文件，招标人不予受理</div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt">5.5未按<span>5.2、5.3要求提供资料的招标人不予受理。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt">本次招标公告同时在<u>《中国政府采购网》</u>、<u>《北京政府采购网》</u>、《<u>中国采购与招标网》、《中国财经报》</u>上发布。</div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><a name="_Toc463856516">6. </a><span>投标供应商在缔约过程中应依法遵守诚实信用原则。</span></font></b></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 15.5pt; margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt 5.05pt"><b>凡是已向本中心报名，并确认参加本项目又不参加此次招标项目的，至少应在招标文件要求提交投标文件的截止时间五日前书面通知招标采购单位；未按规定书面通知招标采购单位的，应属于有悖于诚实信用原则的行为，北京市门头沟区政府采购中心将在一年内拒绝其参加本中心组织的招标活动。</b></div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 21pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 13pt 0cm"><b><font size="5"><a name="_Toc247085678"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">7. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style="line-height: 173%; font-size: 15pt">联系方式</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt" align="left"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: black">采购人：</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: red">北京市门头沟区市政市容管理委员会</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt" align="left"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: black">地 址：</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: red">北京市门头沟区双峪路</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: red">39-1</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: red">号</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt" align="left"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: black">联系人：</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: red">纪寅 &nbsp;联系电话：69843116</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; punctuation-trim: leading"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">招标代理机构：<u>北京市门头沟区政府采购中心</u><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">地<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>址：<u><span style="color: black">北京市门头沟区双峪路39-1</span></u></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">邮<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>编：<u> 102300<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">联 系 人：&nbsp;<u>张芬</u><u>、高奉雯</u><u><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">电<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>话：<u>&nbsp;010-69828192<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">传<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>真：<u><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 010-61805154&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">网<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>址：<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <u>&nbsp;http</u></span><u>：</u><u>//www.bjmtgcg.cn</u><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div>
<div style="line-height: 23pt">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　2017年11月14日</div>
<div style="line-height: 20pt">&nbsp;</div>
